Trainline Logo Trainline is an international digital rail and coach technology platform with headquarters in London, England. It sells train tickets and railcards as well as providing free access to live train times and railway station information through its website and mobile app which is available on the iOS and Android platforms. Listed on the London Stock Exchange, it is a constituent of the FTSE 250 Index. Source
